Name  : Bitcoin gateway integration 4.6.1
URL   : https://secure.qtmsoft.com/customer.php?target=task_info&subject=536882026_461

To apply the changes do the following:
1. Apply the SQL changes (Open the Patch/Upgrade page in admin area and select the patch.sql from the archive for the "Apply SQL patch" section).
2. Apply the code and template changes:
2.1. Either select the patch.diff file for the "Apply patch" section and follow the instructions.
2.2. Or just copy the new files over the old ones. The catalog tree is preserved in the "files" catalog of the archive.
2.3. Copy the images from the "files/skin1/images/" directory to the corresponding directory on your server.
